## Verdict

Reliability improved:

- Probe output now separates native-only and bridge-assisted evidence.
- The probe no longer restarts the bridge when --keep-bridge-running is used.
- The bridge skips common ACK/status response loops as terminal messages.
- Current-age queue drain was verified.

Still not complete:

Native Pentagon handoff activation remains red. T5K does not close the full goal; it makes the audit and bridge mitigation harder to misread while preserving the native blocker.
